history.content:
I was expected to graduate SP 21 with a CS minor but I'm considering just graduating early this semester and give up the minor.

I just have 1 more class to take but feels like a waste of money to spend tuition for just 1 more class. (unfortunately, this semester is loaded for me so I couldn't take another class)

Is the minor worth doing another semester (don't plan on doing SWE, but ironically the degree seems to be valued more in non-technical positions)? I plan on going to grad school in a nontechnical field
history.subject: Graduating early vs CS minor
